      Question:
      Does this charge while its on the magnetic part of the iPad Pro 12
      Answer:
      No, it charges via usb c interface just like smartphones. It comes with a usb c cable, plug it into a usb port, it charges very quickly. When the pencil's battery is charged, embedded chip stops the charging process. There's no way to overcharge the battery of the stylus and charging during the night won't kill it.

      Product description

      Color:Rose Gold

      Stylus Pencil for iPad Pro 2021, iPad Pro 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad Air 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad 8th/7th/6th Generation, iPad mini 5

      Wide Compatibility
      iPad Pro 2021, iPad Pro 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad Air 4th & 3rd Generation, iPad 8th/7th/6th Generation, iPad mini 5.

      IPad Pro, IPad, IPad Air, IPad Mini 2018-2021
      Designed for All iPads launched in 2018 and after.

      How to use
      Press the button to turn on and off.

      Tilt Creative
      This pencil is built in with tilt pressure sensors. The tilt angle reflects the different thickness and concentration of the line.

      Palm Rejection
      You can use the Stylus like a real pencil on paper, rest your palm on the iPad screen.

      Tap the Screen to make a quick note
      Tap your iPad screen with the Stylus to open the Notes app and collect your ideas easily.

      Fast Charging
      Premium Lithium battery. USB C fast charging. 1 minute = 30 minutes to use. Charging time: Less than 1 hour.

      Magnetic
      Can be magnetically stored on the iPad Pro, iPad, iPad Air, iPad mini 2018-2021.

      Pixel precision
      Using advanced technology, the Stylus can accurately locate each pixel of the iPad screen and work like an A pple pencil.

      Easy to use
      Super easy to use. No set up required. Long battery life. Connects immediately. Smooth easy writing.

      Beauty
      High-end elegant durable aluminum unibody design.

      Word-of-mouth
      Customers keep telling us how it exceed their expectations and recommend to check this out before spending the extra money.

      What You Get
      1* AZX Palm Rejection Active Pencil + 2* Additional Replacement Tips + 1* USB C Cable + 1* User manual.

      Warranty
      We Provide 12-Month Warranty AND Lifetime Technical Support.
